• Sử dụng thành thạo tiếng Trung hoặc tiếng Anh trong công việc.

Job Description:
Seven hills trading is an import export company with various line of business in trading of agro-commodities, aquaculture products, animal feed raw materials, fruits, pharmaceuticals and restaurant business. Currently we are searching for a pragmatics candidate to join our company.

- Set-up, implement and monitor accounting system for company group Vietnam accounts and any business project while
ensuring that all accounts and financial reports comply with Government laws and with Company’s policies and procedures;
- Review and sign off as authorized by the Company, on all tax reports - monthly, quarterly and yearly;
- Monitor the implementation of company’s payment procedures to protect company’s interests.
- Authorized for bank accounts and transactions inclusive of payroll and cash transactions;
- Prepare annual budget and monitor expenses based on budget, cash flow forecast monthly and payment plan weekly.
- Coordinate with local external (A company group external auditor and internal auditors for applicable audits and audit reports.
- In charge of tax reporting (PIT, CIT, FCT…), tax inspection and tax returns as per Vietnamese Tax laws;
- Monitor all purchases made while verifying supplier’s quotation in order to issue purchase/work contracts;
- To manage administration works such as set-up office, apply for required licenses / permits & tax codes, new recruitments, etc.;

