Job Description:
Lucky Power Vietnam (Headquater in Shenzhen, China) is a high-tech enterprise focuses on personal care and beauty products, integrating R&D, production and sales. Our current main products in Vietnam market is High-speed New Generation Hair Dryer


- Make short videos and post on Tiktok, Instagram, Facebook, X (Twitter), Youtube, Linkedln. The content posted on different platforms can be same at same day;
- Find and book KOL/KOC, Influencers to cooperate
- Develop part-timers every month (part-time targets need to have more than 1000 followers), forward the posts of our official account according to the part-time agreement, assist Lucky Power brand and product promotion, also help official accounts increase visitors;
- Offline advertising promotion: find suitable venues for Ads such as public sports venue, salons, Ads at large public events &Prize sponsor, Ads with traditional advertiser;...

*** Main responsibilities:
- Managing a client portfolio;
- Communicating with B2B clients, meeting their demands and requirements via skype, emails or phone;
- Advising clients and keeping abreast of the market news and the forthcoming products;
- Elaborating tour programs according to clients’ requests and following the Sales Department procedures;
- Collecting marketing documents and providing additional information to clients (about the destination and the products) in order to boost sales;
